Helper function
Show code 
# Function to remove extreme outliers using 3 * IQR method
remove_extreme_outliers <- function(data, value_column, group_column) {
  data %>%
    group_by({{ group_column }}) %>%
    mutate(
      Q1 = quantile({{ value_column }}, 0.25, na.rm = TRUE),
      Q3 = quantile({{ value_column }}, 0.75, na.rm = TRUE),
      IQR = Q3 - Q1,
      lower_bound = Q1 - 3 * IQR,
      upper_bound = Q3 + 3 * IQR,
      is_outlier = if_else({{ value_column }} < lower_bound | {{ value_column }} > upper_bound, TRUE, FALSE)
    ) %>%
    ungroup()
}

  filter(exposure != "pen_001") %>%  # Remove pen_001
  remove_extreme_outliers(distance_moved, exposure) %>%
  filter(!is_outlier) %>%
  dplyr::select(-Q1, -Q3, -IQR, -lower_bound, -upper_bound, -is_outlier) %>%
  mutate(exposure = as.factor(exposure))

  geom_boxplot(alpha = 0.6, fill="#569A6F", color="#569A6F", outlier.alpha = 0.1) +
  labs(x = "PE NPs (mg/L)", y = "Distance (mm/min)") +
  scale_x_discrete(limits = c("c", "pen_01", "pen_1", "pen_5", "pen_10"),
                   labels = c("C", "0.1", "1", "5", "10"))+
  ylim(0,300)+
  annotate("text", x = 2, y = 290, label = "*", size = 6) +
  annotate("text", x = 3, y = 290, label = "*", size = 6) +
  annotate("text", x = 4, y = 290, label = "*", size = 6) +
  annotate("text", x = 5, y = 290, label = "*", size = 6) +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(panel.grid.major = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank())+
  theme(legend.position = "none")

##### Helper function
```{r}
# Function to remove extreme outliers using 3 * IQR method
remove_extreme_outliers <- function(data, value_column, group_column) {
  data %>%
    group_by({{ group_column }}) %>%
    mutate(
      Q1 = quantile({{ value_column }}, 0.25, na.rm = TRUE),
      Q3 = quantile({{ value_column }}, 0.75, na.rm = TRUE),
      IQR = Q3 - Q1,
      lower_bound = Q1 - 3 * IQR,
      upper_bound = Q3 + 3 * IQR,
      is_outlier = if_else({{ value_column }} < lower_bound | {{ value_column }} > upper_bound, TRUE, FALSE)
    ) %>%
    ungroup()
}
```

  mutate(exposure = as.factor(exposure))


ps_5_act <- behavior_files_list$ps_5_activity

kbl(ps_5_act, format = "html") |>
  kable_styling(
    full_width = FALSE,
    bootstrap_options = c("condensed", "striped")
  ) |>
  scroll_box(height = "300px", width = "100%") 


ps_5_dist_plot <- ggplot(ps_5_clean, aes(x = exposure, y = distance_moved)) +
  geom_boxplot(alpha = 0.6, fill="#934C5D", color="#934C5D", outlier.alpha = 0.1) +
  labs(x = "PS MPs (mg/L)", y = "Distance (mm/min)") +
  scale_x_discrete(limits = c("c", "ps_5_1", "ps_5_10", "ps_5_25", "ps_5_50", "ps_5_75", "ps_5_100"),
                   labels = c("C", "1", "10", "25", "50", "75", "100"))+
  ylim(0,300)+
   annotate("text", x = 2, y = 290, label = "*", size = 6) +
   annotate("text", x = 3, y = 290, label = "*", size = 6) +
   annotate("text", x = 5, y = 290, label = "*", size = 6) +
   annotate("text", x = 7, y = 290, label = "*", size = 6) +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(panel.grid.major = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank())+
  theme(legend.position = "none")

ps_5_dist_plot
